snippet.title: Blade Assault - Official 1.0 Release Trailer
snippet.description:
Enjoy the version 1.0 launch trailer for Blade Assault, the new pixel-art beat-'em-up/shoot-'em-up that's being released on PC (via Steam) on January 17.

#IGN
